claim.claim-text:
5. A turbopump assembly, comprising: 
a catalyst bed for decomposing a material to produce a discharge; 
a mixer section downstream of said catalyst bed for introducing an additional amount of said material to said discharge to produce an exhaust stream having a mass flow; 
a nozzle downstream of said mixer section; 
a turbine downstream of said nozzle; and 
a pump driven by said turbine; 
wherein said additional amount of said material is selected to produce a desired amount of said mass flow.

7. A method of throttling a rocket engine, comprising the steps of: 
providing a catalyst bed; 
introducing an amount of a material into said catalyst bed so that said catalyst bed decomposes said material to produce a discharge; and 
selectively adding an additional amount of said material into said discharge to produce an exhaust stream having a mass flow; 
whereby said additional amount of said material increases said mass flow of said exhaust stream.
